{ project to allow TDBGridEh to sort data in            }
{ TpFIBDataset automatically after sorting markers      }
{ will be changed.                                      }
{ TFIBDatasetFeaturesEh will sort data locally          }
{ using DoSort procedure of TpFIBDataset                }
